plt.dataset

Class ObjectsOrderFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • plt.dataset.ObjectsOrderFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSet

    public class ObjectsOrderFormat
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataSet
    Reader for a 2-file format. Objects file contains the input samples (1 per row) The order file specifies the partial orders between input samples (each row a sequence of IDs, from higher to lower)
    Author:
    Vincent Farrugia, Hector P. Martinez, Luca Querella
